snippet.title: Best VGM 1812 - Sonic Lost World - Sea Bottom Segue
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1936 - https://youtu.be/ro4ceM17QzY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii U
Sonic Lost World (2013)
Sea Bottom Segue
Tomoya Ohtani
